        <title>关于一台老旧Mac变成了最强软路由的这档事</title>
        <link>https://tutuis.me/p/%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%B0%E8%80%81%E6%97%A7mac%E5%8F%98%E6%88%90%E4%BA%86%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%BA%E8%BD%AF%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%99%E6%A1%A3%E4%BA%8B/</link>
